title: 15 Minute Fat Burning HIIT Workout | No Equipment | The Body Coach
description:
3 rounds | 5 exercises | Working for 35 seconds | Rest for 25 seconds

6 High Knees then 4 Lunge Jumps
5 Narrow Press-Ups into 5 wide Press-Ups
5 Toe Touches then 5 Full Body Crunches
6 Mountain Climbers with lateral move
4 Crab Toe Touches then 4 Kick Throughs

comments: I like how you got straight and to the point. No rambling on with long speeches, just a quick intorduction and then straight to business.
I lost more than 100 lbs with this video. Thank you so much. I was 314 pounds, now I weigh 212.6 lbs  and man do I feel good.
I love how he shows examples and then he actually does the workout with the viewer! It's uncut and real! I'm very motivated to do this!

LISTEN UP EVERYONE! STOP DOING THE EXERCISES WITHOUT WARMING UP! Do some swings and stretch your muscles. Thats why you feel tired after a minute. Your muscles and limbs need to be at the right temperature to do it’s max potential. What i do is some light swing-exercises and to get my pulse up i do some jumps. Then i round it off with some shadow boxing. Hope you found this helpful!

EDIT: Remember to drink as much water as your body needs an hour or two before. Remember the 1-2 method. Eat and drink 1 to 2 hours before working out.

35/25 (3 Rounds)
6 high knees 4 lunge jumps
5 narrow 5 wide press-ups
5 toe touches 5 full body crunch
6 mountain climbers 2 side step
4 crab toe touch 4 kick through
